divs: Sighting Detailswent out back looked up and saw 2 beautiful objects...square shape. 5 lights...2red in front, 2green in back 1 bright,clear in mid-section but no body. i looked for a cabin cause i thought it was a plain. but no body to it. no sound whatsoever. they were flying dangerously close. not as high a plane would fly. coming right toward me. i listened but no sound. freaky but beautiful object. flew over my house slowly and then gone... please have a mufon investigator contact me. thank you. nancy
